      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan documented, version control enforced, and independent code review completed for hemolysis solver modules.",
      "rationale": "Version control is in place but independent code review of the hemolysis damage accumulation modules has not been completed. SQA plan exists at draft level only. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
