      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests completed for all governing equations including hemolysis transport; manufactured solutions applied.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not extended to the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Manufactured solution verification is absent for the damage accumulation model. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5."
