      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study was completed and GCI reported for pressure and velocity QoIs. However, GCI for the hemolysis index itself was not reported separately. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
