      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometry, flow regime, and fluid properties sufficiently similar to the VAD COU; similarity metrics quantified.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry which shares topological similarity with the target VAD but differs in impeller diameter and volute design. Flow regime similarity is partial; hematocrit and viscosity matched but RBC deformability not controlled. Achieved level 3 is below required level 5."
