      "rationale": "No independent review of model setup or boundary condition assignment was performed. Post-processing scripts for hemolysis index computation have not been independently verified. Factor flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification provided for selection of hemolysis damage model (power-law vs. strain-based); sensitivity of predictions to model form alternatives quantified.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was selected without documented justification or comparison to alternative model forms such as the Arora strain-based model. Model form uncertainty is unquantified. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
