      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ propagated through hemolysis predictions with reported confidence intervals.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input parameter distributions for blood viscosity, hematocrit, and hemolysis model coefficients were assigned based on literature ranges rather than patient-specific measurements. Propagated uncertainty intervals are not reported in the submission. Factor flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
