      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples (blood or blood analog) characterized for relevant properties; lot-to-lot variability documented; sample preparation protocol traceable.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood was used in validation experiments but lot characterization data (hematocrit, MCV, plasma viscosity) are not reported. Sample preparation protocol is described qualitatively only. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
