      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis was performed between validation inputs (bovine blood, bench-scale flow loop) and COU inputs (human blood, implanted VAD operating conditions). Extrapolation from bench to in-vivo conditions is unaddressed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
